com.aptima.netstorm.algorithms.aptima.bp.network

Class AdjacencyListNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aptima.netstorm.algorithms.aptima.bp.network.AdjacencyListNode
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AttributedDataNode, AttributedModelNode

    public class AdjacencyListNode
extends java.lang.Object
    Basic network node that stores a list of predecessors and successors with an id. Other node types should extend this class if they need to store additional algorithm specific information. The node optionally stores attribute information via an AttributeSet.

    jroberts
